    "Overall, it is fair to say that the same conclusions can be drawn from the SVDs of the original and reduced data.",
    "(a) x-component (b) y-component Flow around an aircraftWe finally consider the flow around an aircraft half-model to demonstrate the potential of S 3 to efficiently reduce extremely large amounts of data.",
